{
 "name": "RPlog_Masquerade_Ball_A_Night_on_Yavin_Part_2",
 "title": "Masquerade Ball: A Night on Yavin (Part 2)",
 "summary": "The tropical masquerade aboard the Angry Rancor continues in full swing as Inanna dances with the totem-headed Ramyxth and her sister Sel returns to the stage with island songs. Ka'una conspires with the costumed pirate Juran, who has arrived in a ridiculous Piranha-Beetle helmet, to nudge attention toward the dancing pair. New guests slip in, including the quiet, orange-clad Lepidoptera, the blue-winged Kyrin Sh'vani, Shael in a borrowed blue dress, and a soft-spoken Rebel pilot whose voice eerily resembles Luke Skywalker. The mingling, drinking, and good-natured ribbing build the festive atmosphere as more masked identities begin to be guessed at.",
